				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="2">A wake in honor of Heilgae (Fennin Ro)</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:j.vastenhout@chello.nl">Aaeilae Ravenstar</b></a>
				[11/6/2001-11:44:23 AM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=516073"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[5]</font></a><p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><blockquote>
  <p>OSR has been asked to host a wake in honor of Heilgae. Heilgae having been a very active player in EQ had explored with, adventurered with, partied with, and befriended a great many people on the Fennin Ro server.<br>
  While I do not have details of how he passed away in real life... I want to stress the how isn't important. What is important is that a person, a friend to many, has now gone on to whatever lie beyond this existance. We should gather to remember him.<br>
  <br>
  Although in real life I suspect he was apt to drinking and having fun I also believe from what I knew of him to be conservative enough to not let it get out off hand... HOWEVER.... he did play a barbarian warrior in game and I can think of no better way to remember him than to have us all gather in permafrost and drink till we can't see. We'll gather at the large cave leading to BB. This spot is large to facilitate us all and is close to Heilgae's birth place.<br>
  <br>
  Please bring all the liquor you can.<br>
  <br>
  During the event I would like to have every person tell ONE thing they remember of Heilgae. It can be a bit of heroism such as 'He could single path pull the plane of hate.' Or somthing as simple as 'I remember the dirty lymrics he came up with at the last Naggy raid.' Just any one thing that you can remember about him.<br>
  <br>
  Where: In Everfrost in the cave leading to BB.<br>
  When: This Sunday 11-11-01. 6pm PST.<br>
  Who: All of the many friends of Heilgae.<br>
  Why: To remember Heilgae. And to get blind drunk.<br>
  <br>
  A friend of Heilgae</p>
</blockquote></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
