  <p>Last night (Nov 2, around 2-4 AM MST), GM Event spawned in Qeynos Hills and Everfrost on the Vazaelle Server.  Probably a layover from the Hallowe'en Events.  Qeynos Hills spawned skeleton soldiers and the like while in Everfrost (where I was) the goddess Elleas tried an invasion of lowlevel werewolves and spectres.  These werewolves (rarely) and spectres (commonly) dropped class only items such as a cleric/druid/shaman Pegasus Headdress ac4 wis4 mana4 disease 4.  Very nice and very shiny!<br>
  <br>
  Ardath Senjak, 26 Woodelf Ranger</p>
