				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="23">Server Maintenance on Ayonae Ro, Zebuxoruk, and Firiona Vie</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:korenth@everlore.com">Korenth</b></a>
				[11/1/2001-11:15:58 AM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=514353"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[1]</font></a><p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">This new update is now in the developer's corner on the offical everquest forums:<br>
<blockquote>
  <p>On Monday, November 5th, at 3AM PST, (11AM GMT), the Ayonae Ro server will
  be brought down for scheduled maintenance. The estimated downtime is 6 hours.
  <p>On Tuesday, November 6th, at 3AM PST, (11AM GMT), the Zebuxoruk server will
  be brought down for scheduled maintenance. The estimated downtime is 4 hours.
  <p>On Wednesday, November 7th, at 3AM PST, (11AM GMT), all servers will be
  brought down for a scheduled patch. The estimated downtime is 7 hours.
  <p>On Thursday, November 8th, at 3AM PST, (11AM GMT), the Firiona Vie server
  will be brought down for scheduled maintenance. The estimated downtime is 4
  hours.
  <p>The EverQuest Operations Team</p>
</blockquote>
You can find this for yourself <a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/Forum1/HTML/000370.html"><b>here!</b></a></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
