				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="29">Patch Update - Oct 31, 2001</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:korenth@everlore.com">Korenth</b></a>
				[10/31/2001-10:29:08 AM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=513910"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[33]</font></a><p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">Here is the patch message from this mornings patch:<br>
<blockquote>
  <p>October 31th, 3:00 am<br>
  ------------------------------<br>
  <br>
  *By the pricking of my thumbs*<br>
  <br>
  - A con man in The Temple of Solusek Ro has been warned by the gods not to tease people about special weapons.<br>
  - Forest Barley can be found now, if you like that sort of thing.<br>
  - There are fewer blind frogloks in Guk.<br>
  - Small trees will fall more frequently in one of the Karanas<br>
  - Be careful in your travels over the next few days.  Something is amiss on Norrath.<br>
  <br>
  Trick or treat!<br>
  <br>
  - The EverQuest Team</p>
</blockquote>
