				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="31">GM Event on Morrel Thule</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:">Xban Passmore</b></a>
				[10/31/2001-8:50:55 AM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=513950"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[6]</font></a><p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><blockquote>
  <p>On this day thy hunting party's hast moved tho hunt to Eastern Karana's.</p>
  <p>Upon zoning in I saw the most forsaken thing in all thee Realms. The Graveyard pawn a
  fierce warrior but he had no match against my friend. His master had brought his
  legions to slay on the week and helpless. But at that very moment a band of hero's rose in our mists. they
  stalked him to his hiding hole and splayed him with the ease of a bixie. But his unholy
  legion's were angered of this and rose him back to slay all of those that had killed him. Many of his undead minion's had stolen items from a Paladin
  near High Hold Keep zone in the gorge but no one could give him his things back.</p>
  <p>Many things came of this GM event and mad many look into there heart deepest place and pull
  courage from no were to fight everything they could<br>
  the things that dropped were mostly no drop items but reports from friend's in Rathe Mountain's That a dragon had landed to slay all that entered the zone. many lives were lost and many were ah stuke by the beauty this veil beast had. In all my loot was Syche's of many kinds Bronze, Rusty's and one plan Syche and a Bronze Cloak. A nice man gave me right's to loot his kill for on him was a
  Shield only of paladin's. lots of money was dropped I got 8pp off one kill but almost lost my life as well.<br>
 Of this fight here are my Camera's point of view.</p>
  <p>Also one other note a lot of KSing from high lvl 50+ sometime mad the thing go bad.
  I got KSed by Kesta a mage that could care less bout friendship just money and loot. But in all it was the best thing
  I had ever done.<br>
  <br>
  Thanks go to Derg (Druid) sowing me on the run from mobs<br>
  Wolfywolf the port and telling me about it  and last but not lest to the guy and lady that saved my butt at the Bridge
  I didn't get you name but thank you.<br>
  <br>
  Xban Passmore (Paladin)<br>
  24th sword <Seekers of the Path></p>
</blockquote></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
