				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="32">GM event in EK on Test</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:qball69_1@hotmail.com">Boredorm</b></a>
				[10/31/2001-7:27:45 AM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=513846"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[1]</font></a><p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><blockquote>
  <p>Late on Monday night around 12pm to 2am there was a GM event in Ek it all started with the sky turning red and alot of shouting from some werid named mobs, no one know what was going on all we know was something was a miss next thing we knew named Specs.,EE's, giant skeletons, and named human casters of all kinds they where droping class/race related stuff all in all it was quite fun thanks for the GM's that were up this late for remembering us</p>
</blockquote>
</font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
